dashboard_elements.body_text:
The 8 top google search queries were chosen based on the total number of impressions as of Oct 27. There was a clear cut-off at 8 as each had more than 100K impressions at that time. The reports below will continue past that date. If needed, we can update the included terms.

These 8 queries include the top 4 queries by number of clicks which all had more than 10K clicks (with the 5th top query dropping to 5K clicks) at that time.
